[h2]v0.13.0 — Living Market Scaffolding & Defensive pcall Migration[/h2]
[list]
[*] Living Market Layer 0 scaffolding — autonomous economy framework with agent archetypes, wholesaler system, market zones, and supply pressure modeling (gated by sandbox option, not yet active)
[*] 3 new shared modules: POS_MarketAgent, POS_WholesalerService, POS_MarketSimulation
[*] Comprehensive Living Market constants — 7 agent archetypes, 6 market zones, 6 market event types, 6 wholesaler operational states
[*] ~37 POSnet defensive pcalls migrated to PhobosLib.safecall for Strict Mode compatibility
[*] Fixed logic error in POS_TutorialService.migrateLegacy() (line 205)
[*] Replaced local math utilities with PhobosLib equivalents (clamp, lerp, randFloat)
[*] Updated design guidelines with Living Market module references and Strict Mode pcall patterns
[*] PhobosLib 1.48.0 dependency (new math/table utilities)
[*] Full translation infrastructure for Living Market entities (agents, zones, events, states, signals)
[/list]

[h2]v0.10.0 — Danger Detection, Cache Externalization & Polish (Preview)[/h2]
