[*] Auto-migration from old ModData caches on first load
[*] Unique Raw Market Note icon (folded paper with field notes aesthetic)
[*] Dynamic tooltips via PhobosLib.registerTooltipProvider() — notes show category, items, prices
[*] Journal/document writing system for in-game readable intel
[*] Item name filtering for display names (removes "Base." prefix)
[*] Iteration history document (ITERATION_HISTORY.md)
[*] DangerCheckRadius sandbox option (default 15, range 5-30)
[*] Tooltip.json created (fixes raw key display in item tooltips)
[*] PhobosLib 1.40.0 dependency (danger detection, document writing, tooltip providers)
[/list]

